title: Hackers Claiming to Jailbreak AI Chatbots to Write Phishing Emails
description:
By Deeba Ahmed

Cybercriminals on multiple hacker forums claim to jailbreak AI chatbots to write malicious content, including phishing emails, a new report from SlashNext has revealed.

title: Contractor Data Breach Impacts 8k Greater Manchester Police Officers
description:
By Deeba Ahmed

Warrant card details of thousands of officers are suspected to have been stolen in this attack. Affected officers have been notified about the data breach.
